{%- comment -%} Perf: warm up Shopify CDN and preload Spitzkant 
   Custom heading font family override (Spitzkant)
   Use Spitzkant for all heading families via theme variables
   We keep Theme Editor typography controls (sizes/weights/spacing), but force
   heading font-family to Spitzkant across the theme.
   If theme updates ever rename these variables, re-apply this block.
{%- endcomment -%}

<link rel="preload" as="font" type="font/woff2"
  href="{{ 'spitzkant-head-regular.woff2' | asset_url }}"
  crossorigin>

<style>
@font-face{
  font-family: 'Spitzkant';
  src:
    url('{{ 'spitzkant-head-regular.woff2' | asset_url }}') format('woff2'),
    url('{{ 'spitzkant-head-regular.woff'  | asset_url }}') format('woff');
  font-weight: 400;   /* you own regular only */
  font-style: normal;
  font-display: swap;
}
</style>

